🚀 Day 08/30 – Random Quote Generator

Continuing my 30 Days JavaScript Challenge, I built a modern Quote Generator Web App using Vanilla JavaScript.

🛠️ Tech Used:

• HTML • CSS • Vanilla JavaScript

✨ Features:

• Generate random quotes from API
• Displays quote with author
• Dark / Light mode toggle (with local storage)
• Theme persistence on reload
• One-click copy to clipboard
• Loading state while fetching data
• Fallback quote on API error
• Fully responsive design
• Smooth UI interactions

📚 What I Learned:

• Fetch API with async/await
• Handling API errors gracefully
• DOM manipulation & event handling
• Clipboard API usage
• Theme toggling with localStorage
• Writing cleaner and reusable JS logic
• Working with real-world APIs

🚀 Next Improvements:

• Share quote (Twitter / WhatsApp)
• Add categories / filters
• Favorite / save quotes
• Toast notifications
• Quote transition animations
• Text-to-Speech feature

🌐 Live

